textBody:
There are several places named Kinderhook in the United States:

Places

* Kinderhook, Illinois, a village in Pike County
* Kinderhook Creek, a tributary of the Hudson River
* Kinderhook (town), New York, in Columbia County
** Kinderhook (village), New York, in the above town
* Kinderhook, Ohio, an unincorporated community
* Kinderhook Township, Pike County, Illinois
* Kinderhook Township, Michigan, in Branch County

Other

*"Old Kinderhook", a name applied to U.S. President Martin Van Buren
*Kinderhook plates, a hoax perpetrated on 19th century Mormons
